text_lines.line_text: PH - The pH of a 50% concentration of A32 in a 52.6% dioxane/water
solution was calculated to be 2.92 at 22℃ according to the extra-
polation procedures by Dr. P. D. Schickedantz, Lorillard Research
Oral - 5g A32 forms a suspension with stirring in 10 ml 1% Tween 80
Acute Cardiovascular - Mix 2 mg A32 with 0.2 ml 80% propylene glycol
and grind lightly. Add 0.8 ml saline solution. A32 is a suspension
in this mixture at room temperature.
